the closet, here, okay?

04:20.453 --> 04:22.357
-What?!
-BOB: Love you.

04:23.426 --> 04:25.196
-It's okay, it's okay.
-(scoffs)

04:25.196 --> 04:27.602
-Hey, Bob?
-BOB: Yes'm?

04:27.602 --> 04:31.275
So, so, fishing stuff is
kind of, like, garage materials.

04:31.275 --> 04:34.949
You know, the closets are, like,
for fancy s... fancy things.

04:34.949 --> 04:36.520
BOB: Oh. Okay, got it.

04:37.588 --> 04:40.393
(whispers): Thank you.

04:40.393 --> 04:42.397
-I feel so seen.
-(chuckles)

04:44.936 --> 04:46.673
Any word from James?

04:48.644 --> 04:50.346
I'm sure he will
be here any minute.

04:51.382 --> 04:53.319
