Is he not reliable?

04:53.319 --> 04:55.323
You can be late
and be reliable.

04:55.323 --> 04:57.662
Yes, of course.
Of course you can.

04:57.662 --> 04:59.566
And he's done all that work.

04:59.566 --> 05:01.636
Right? So, yes, of course.

05:01.636 --> 05:03.406
-He is reliable.
-(clears throat)

05:03.406 --> 05:05.778
You know what?

05:05.778 --> 05:08.216
