05:14.729 --> 05:17.234
You got your license back.

05:18.302 --> 05:19.772
Thank you.

05:20.808 --> 05:23.079
Just... Fill it, give it a wash.

05:23.079 --> 05:25.718
-You got it.
-Thank you. Yeah.

05:25.718 --> 05:28.222
-See you.
-Yeah, bye.

05:28.222 --> 05:30.226
