I did not like that, though.

06:36.979 --> 06:39.652
I was very scared
and very worried.

06:39.652 --> 06:42.256
-We all were.
-I'm sorry.

06:42.256 --> 06:46.097
Well, I'm gonna go see if my
name is at the singles table.

06:47.300 --> 06:49.203
JAMES:
Do you want to banish me there,
too? It's totally fine,

06:49.203 --> 06:51.809
-I don't mind.
-Have you seen yourself
in this suit?

06:51.809 --> 06:54.213
-You're not going anywhere
near the singles table.
-Hi, guys.

06:54.213 --> 06:57.219
Samantha. Uh, so, I was just
spreading the word.

06:57.219 --> 06:59.190
