running a little behind

06:59.190 --> 07:01.261
on, like, backstage stuff.

07:02.964 --> 07:04.935
So while we just
try and take care of things,

07:04.935 --> 07:07.106
we're gonna go on ahead
and get the hors d'oeuvres going

07:07.106 --> 07:09.277
so you don't starve
before the ceremony, okay?

07:09.277 --> 07:11.549
