-Yes, lots

07:11.549 --> 07:15.289
of drinks, and
I'll be back soon, hopefully.

07:15.289 --> 07:16.759
What the hell
did she mean by that?

07:16.759 --> 07:18.730
I don't know.
I think I should go find Brit.

07:20.967 --> 07:23.740
-Here.
-No. People are gonna
think we're together.

07:23.740 --> 07:25.242
All right.

07:29.183 --> 07:30.754
(door opens)

07:30.754 --> 07:33.158
-She's here. She's here.
-Oh, my God.

07:33.158 --> 07:34.528
-Hi.
-Hi. Thank you for coming.

07:34.528 --> 07:36.599
Honestly, it was an emergency.

07:36.599 --> 07:38.703
Sure. (short chuckle)
Always on call,

07:38.703 --> 07:40.940
even when I'm technically
not on the schedule

07:40.940 --> 07:44.380
and been, you know, my first
day off in three weeks, so...

07:44.380 --> 07:46.819
Is that the dress?
I'm not-I'm not looking.

07:46.819 --> 07:48.288
Ooh, but I want to kiss you.

07:53.633 --> 07:55.904
-Okay, go, go.
-Yes, absolutely.

07:57.006 --> 07:58.810
So, what is the problem?

07:58.810 --> 08:00.980
Well, you know,
the dress doesn't fit.

08:00.980 --> 08:03.351
-Oh, it does.
-No.

08:03.351 --> 08:05.022
We had four fittings,

08:05.022 --> 08:07.159
