08:10.867 --> 08:13.506
Oh, yeah, well, you just
need to zip it up.

08:13.506 --> 08:15.442
-Okay, well, all right...
-Oh, no,

08:15.442 --> 08:17.848
-no, stop. Oh, stop. Ooh.
-But...

08:17.848 --> 08:21.254
