all in when I say "suck it."

08:21.254 --> 08:23.458
-Okay, that's not my favorite.
-Okay. But...

08:23.458 --> 08:25.162
suck it.

08:25.162 --> 08:26.599
There you go. Yeah, see?
Fits perfectly.

08:26.599 --> 08:28.603
-And you look...
-Wrong. Wrong.

08:28.603 --> 08:30.339
Wrong. Just unzip it.
Unzip it,

08:30.339 --> 08:33.011
-unzip it, please,
unzip it, unzip it.
-Okay, okay.

08:34.515 --> 08:36.017
