you say it like that, but yes.

09:25.082 --> 09:27.487
Okay. Go.

09:27.487 --> 09:28.856
Suck it, suck it,
suck it, suck it,

09:28.856 --> 09:31.996
-suck it, suck it,
suck it, suck...
-Oh, my God!

09:31.996 --> 09:35.536
-No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.
